translation.Name: Rula Note - Forklifts
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: Zero accidents this month... I have a feeling this number will soon change seeing how our forklifts are being used by the crew. Those things seriously need a speed governor.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_4: I'll place some posters about forklift safety in the facility, and I'll also have a meeting with staff that are forklift certified.
